channel.title: Raffy Tulfo in Action
channel.description:
Welcome to the OFFICIAL Youtube channel of Raffy Tulfo! 

Raffy Tulfo is a Filipino broadcast journalist based in Mandaluyong City, Philipines. He is a hard-hitting, no-holds-barred commentator on issues pertaining to abuses and injustices committed by people in power against ordinary citizens.

He is a known champion of the poor. He fights for the downtrodden – many of whom are laborers – who flock to his radio show everyday to seek for his help. He is known among his followers as “Mr. Action Man” and “Idol Raffy”.

Raffy Tulfo is the main anchor of a long existing top rated radio program WANTED SA RADYO aired on 92.3 FM (Radyo5) and simulcast on OnePH. He also anchors AKSYON SA TANGHALI, a noontime newscast that is aired daily on TV5. The said newscast has a public service segment– Itimbre mo kay Tulfo/Ipa-Raffy Mo, that airs and acts on complaints from ordinary citizens.

Get ready to witness the life changing public service in action.

snippet.title: Magpakailanman: Married man lives with his two wives | Full Episode
snippet.description:
While George (Luis Alandy) and Francia (Glaiza De Castro) are living happily in their marriage, their once peaceful life together gets derailed upon the arrival of the former's first love, Oli (Pauleen Luna). Soon after, George decides to let Oli stay with them after finding out that the latter is getting abused by her partner. Will Francia be able to keep up with this kind of setup—living with her husband and his first love under one roof?

Watch this video and more exclusive full episodes of 'Magpakailanman' on https://bit.ly/2XJyJoG
